Veteran media personality Fred Obachi Machoka was a proud daddy, when his son, Santos wed the love of his life at an exotic location.The wedding took place in Cancun, Mexico, where family jetted in for the event from Kenya.The Roga Roga grandmaster announced the news on his social media."An ordinary visit to Cancun Mexico should be fun, but an extraordinary one like the one we made, is just beyond description!" he wrote on his social media pages.Adding: "Friends, please allow me to use this platform to convey my heartfelt congratulations to my loving son, Santos, for finding the love of his life, Carla McQueen, to share a future with. May the Almighty God light your path now and Always."